milestones.description: Dean Jones's 145 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for AUS), surpassing Greg Chappell's 138
Dean Jones has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (72) in an innings in ODIs for AUS, going past Geoff Marsh's 66
Dean Jones and Geoff Marsh's 185-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 178 between Dean Jones and Geoff Marsh
